fields.name: Navy Arrow Print Drawstring Bag
fields.description:
This arrow themed drawstring bag can be used for children's PE Kits, Nursery Bag, School Bag, adults Sports Bag or Beach Bag. The Size is great for children to take to school to hold spare clothes, shoes or to generally use as a backpack. The Bag is strong and a good size so can hold quite a lot.
The Bag is fully lined. The bag is not waterproof.

The bag can be machine washed at 30. It cannot be tumble-dried or dry cleaned.

The bag is finished with 2 drawstring cords that you use to close and open the bag as well as straps for easy wear.

fields.name: Navy Blue Chevron Cotton Drawstring Bag
fields.description:
This Navy Chevron Drawstring bag is perfect for children to take to school or nursery, or to use as a PE bag or hold spare clothes, shoes or to generally use as a backpack. The Bag is strong and a good size so can hold quite a lot.
The Outer fabric is made with 100% cotton fabric.
The Bag is fully lined inside with 100% Polyester white satin fabric.
This Bag is NOT waterproof.
The Bag can be washed at 30 degrees or on a low heat. Please do not tumble dry or bleach the bag.
The bag is finished with 2 drawstring cords that you use to close and open the bag as well as straps for easy wear.
The Bag size is 35cm wide X 45cm high - 14 inches wide X 18 inches high
